IntelliKart
//landing_page strings Intellikart...An initiative for smart shopping Please follow the following steps to enjoy our initiative for smart shopping : 1) Scan the cart you choose using the QR code scanner 2) Start shopping for the items that you want. 3) When you have shopped for 10 items, a message will pop up asking you for confirmation as to whether you would want to purchase those 10 items 4) If you click on "Yes" , your items will be transferred to the permanent cart. If you click on "NO", then scan the item that you want to remove and click on the remove button. Continue shopping till you have shopped for 10 items again. 5) Once you have completed your shopping, click on the end shopping button and complete the payment 6) Once your payment is confirmed, get it verified by the security and you could head towards the exit Happy Shopping!!! Continue
